ctionCredentials&quot;,&quot;IsPublic&quot;:false,&quot;Settings&quot;:{&quot;Selection&quot;:&quot;Single&quot;,&quot;Type&quot;:&quot;Database&quot;},&quot;Validation&quot;:[],&quot;Groups&quot;:null,&quot;Parameters&quot;:[],&quot;Conditions&quot;:[{&quot;TypeStr&quot;:&quot;DnnSharp.Common2.Services.PlantAnApp.ConfigConditions.IsPlantAnApp,DnnSharp.Common2&quot;,&quot;Settings&quot;:{}}]},{&quot;For&quot;:null,&quot;NotFor&quot;:null,&quot;Id&quot;:&quot;ConnectionString&quot;,&quot;Title&quot;:{&quot;default&quot;:&quot;Override Connection String&quot;},&quot;HelpText&quot;:{&quot;default&quot;:&quot;By default, the SQL will run against the built-in database or the selected Connection. Use this field to override the connection string. Also supports the name of a connection string from the web.config. It will respect the Provider (ODBC, SqlClient, etc.). Can contain Tokens. Read more about &amp;lt;a href=\&quot;http://www.connectionstrings.com/\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&amp;gt;supported formats&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;.&quot;},&quot;Placeholder&quot;:null,&quot;DefaultValue&quot;:null,&quot;Default&quot;:null,&quot;Type&quot;:&quot;Text&quot;,&quot;IsPublic&quot;:false,&quot;Settings&quot;:{},&quot;Validation&quot;:[],&quot;Groups&quot;:null,&quot;Parameters&quot;:[],&quot;Conditions&quot;:[]},{&quot;For&quot;:null,&quot;NotFor&quot;:null,&quot;Id&quot;:&quot;QueryTimeout&quot;,&quot;Title&quot;:{&quot;default&quot;:&quot;Query Timeout&quot;},&quot;HelpText&quot;:{&quot;default&quot;:&quot;Set a time in seconds after which a query will time out. The default is set 10 minutes or 600 seconds also this parameter can&#39;t be negative or under 10 seconds. Can contain Tokens. &quot;},&quot;Placeholder&quot;:null,&quot;DefaultValue&quot;:null,&quot;Default&quot;:null,&quot;Type&quot;:&quot;Text&quot;,&quot;IsPublic&quot;:false,&quot;Settings&quot;:{},&quot;Validation&quot;:[],&quot;Groups&quot;:null,&quot;Parameters&quot;:[],&quot;Conditions&quot;:[]},{&quot;For&quo